setNewScreenSize: aPoint 	"Ensure that the Display is set to the given extent."	self hostWindowExtent: aPoint.	self checkForNewScreenSize.	"In the Windows version of the host window plugin, the extent	currently includes window decorations. Therefore, we need two	attempts to ensure that the Display extent is aPoint. Note that this is	a bug in the plugin."	(Display extent x < aPoint x			or: [Display extent y < aPoint y])		ifTrue: [self hostWindowExtent: 2 * aPoint - Display extent.			self checkForNewScreenSize]